        <h2  >鐵之貝克不想怂的影评 &nbsp; &middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
        <span class="pl">( <a href="http://movie.douban.com/people/congcongimayday/reviews?cat_id=1002">2篇</a> )</span></h2>
        
        <div class="comment-item">
            <div class="pic">
                <a href="http://movie.douban.com/subject/3358309/" title="Lost and Found"><img src="http://img3.douban.com/spic/s4701187.jpg" alt="Lost and Found"></a>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <h3>
                    <a title="失乐园" href="http://movie.douban.com/review/4908254/" class="title">失乐园</a>
                </h3>
                <div class="author">
                    <a href="http://movie.douban.com/people/congcongimayday/">鐵之貝克不想怂</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;评论:&nbsp;<a href="http://movie.douban.com/subject/3358309/">Lost and Found</a>
                </div>
                <p>当听到 lonely ，配上小企鹅和小男孩拥抱的相片，说不出是心酸还是感动。
越大越想看这样纯粹的东西，却也越不敢看。小时候看白雪公主美人鱼，看三个火枪手，看美少女战士。海边小镇大森林城堡王子玩具宠物是我们梦中出现的美丽场景，幻想着长大后我会怎样怎样。谁知道，长大后我就成了你。。。这时候才发现海边可能只...<a href="http://movie.douban.com/review/4908254/">(0回应)</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
